data.title: THE BEST OF THE DOUG GOTTLIEB SHOW - The Doug Gottlieb Show
meta_keywords: THE BEST OF THE DOUG GOTTLIEB SHOW
data.meta_description:
On a Friday edition of The Best Of The Doug Gottlieb Show: Doug weighs in on the recent information that the camp for Caleb Williams, opposed to prior reports, insists they are not anti-Bears.  

Doug reacts to John Harbaugh's recent comments that Lamar Jackson is going to have more say in the offensive scheme next year, and why this proves Lamar doesn't quite know who he is yet.  

Doug welcomes former Bucs' GM Mark Dominik onto the show to talk about the Jim Harbaugh fit with the Chargers, Lamar Jackson and all of the other major headlines around the NFL.

data.text:
On a Friday edition of The Best Of The Doug Gottlieb Show: Doug weighs in on the recent information that the camp for Caleb Williams, opposed to prior reports, insists they are not anti-Bears.

Doug reacts to John Harbaugh's recent comments that Lamar Jackson is going to have more say in the offensive scheme next year, and why this proves Lamar doesn't quite know who he is yet.

Doug welcomes former Bucs' GM Mark Dominik onto the show to talk about the Jim Harbaugh fit with the Chargers, Lamar Jackson and all of the other major headlines around the NFL.
